oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: James Lee Vineyard, Robert L. Butler, Charles Smith, George N. Mize, and Beecher Mize standing in front of the Mize & Son Planing Mill
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The men are standing in front of the G. N. Mize and Son Planing Mill which was located at Sevierville Road and Brown Creek. (L to R) James Lee Vineyard, Robert L. Butler, Charles Smith, George N. Mize (1874-1944), Beecher Mize (1893-1957).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Lumber; Lumber industry; Mills
